{"tid":765201,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我老婆以為我想毒死佢","createTime":"2018-08-02T14:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T16:17:06.000Z","uid":17677,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3824f3c890b23a537a2108ad37ad270857b981","tid":765201,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/222125_9a15ed10d96ddebaeb021877228b6c5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F222125_9a15ed10d96ddebaeb021877228b6c5e.png&h=eaf5d4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上個星期日買左滿記俾佢食<br />\n前日send左依段新聞俾我睇<br />\n係咁屌我係咪好憎佢<br />\n因乜事同佢過唔去要毒死佢<br />\n岩岩返屋企佢又話想食糖水<br />\n我話買滿記好無 佢即刻上哂身咁屌鳩我<br />\n我話其他野無事架 佢嬲到趕撚左我出街<br />\n叫我食滿記食到死撚左佢<br />\n搞到我依家要落九龍城買嚐樂俾佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41bbdcf9f177d98ae63d3b995482a53a95434fd","tid":765201,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ede4b5e498df9d306069445908dc398e27edf06","tid":765201,"uid":139381,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"唔好笑 <br />\n抽得好差"},{"pid":"922f8cdc11d80dd7c72d0782d2fae3ae7895f371","tid":765201,"uid":50932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"今次麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386a76b2b38114b7c1233e17ceed23132f61ba2f","tid":765201,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"振夫綱啦"},{"pid":"966aecaa86580255ff6cb24f02a7eecf8a745042","tid":765201,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T16:05:3